                </div>

                <ul class="media-meta-info list-unstyled list-inline clearfix highlited-item-title-meta">
                        <li class="date">

<div class="time-wrapper"><time datetime="2020-07-05T00:00:00.000" class="">2020. július 5.</time></div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="category">
                            Sajt&#243;k&#246;zlem&#233;ny
                        </li>
                </ul>
                    <h3 class="h4">
                        <a href="/hu/press/press-releases/2020/07/05/climate-transition-transformation-and-convergence-europe-s-path-towards-robust-resilience-speech-of-president-charles-michel/" class="highlited-item-title-link" itemprop="url">&#201;ghajlatv&#233;delmi &#225;t&#225;ll&#225;s, &#225;talakul&#225;s &#233;s konvergencia: Eur&#243;pa &#250;tja a szil&#225;rd reziliencia fel&#233;</a>
                    </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 col-half-tablet pos-r">
